title: DDFP 230: Super Bowl Recap Planecast
itunes:title: DDFP 230: Super Bowl Recap Planecast
description:
On the NFL's chartered flight back to Los Angeles, Shek, Rank, Handsome Hank and Daniel Jeremiah record (probably) the world's first ever planecast. Topics include the results of Super Bowl XLVIII, Peyton Manning's legacy following his poor performance, future of the Seattle Seahawks and a debate of which two teams will be competing in the big game next year.
